    "We find that these penalties operate beautifully in practice and use them to swiftly create high-resolution generative image models for various datasets\".Rezaei et al. [62] identified a unique ensemble-GAN, or generative multi-adversarial network to address the issue of misclassification when it comes to the semantic segmentation of visuals of the abdomen.",
    "The Ensemble-GAN framework incorporated a single generator and a multi-discriminator variant for the purpose of addressing the class imbalance dilemma.",
